text.tspan: “I wish I could ensure every ingredients I’ve purchased are natural and healthy”
Yichun is a full-time housewife with 2 kids. Her husband is
an engineer in high-tech company. With her husband’s
income, they live a life above average level. Shopping and
cooking is the main routine of her life. She always cooks
every meal at home. As a mother, she cares about the
health of her kids. She will pick every ingredients carefully
to make her family has balance, nutritious and toxic-free
diet. Moreover, Yichun also cares about environment, she
is willing to pay a little bit higher price to buy eco-friendly or
At weekend or long vacation, Yichun and her husband
usually take their kids to get touch with nature. She always
thinks that there’s only benefit to be close to nature.
However, as residents of city, they don’t have much chance
to do it. Thus, they seize every time to go to forest or beach
near Hsinchu city and have fun there.
• Purchase natural and safe fresh foods
• Provide sound environment for kids to grow up
• Unsure products are harmful to body
• Have hard time to find place to get close
